And those are the ones we kind of want to bypass because they're kind of uncomfortable, and you really don't know what it is.

00:27:11.862 --> 00:27:24.428
It's like, 'I don't know about that scripture,'but those two scriptures kind of go together, and you go, 'Hmm, what is He really saying there?'And that's why I thought, 'I don't want that question in my mind.

00:27:24.429 --> 00:27:32.010
All I want to know is that I am all in.'And I want you to know that you're all in today, that you're just sold out to Jesus.

00:27:32.011 --> 00:27:35.245
