00:27:44.026 --> 00:28:05.498
I thought it was interesting also that Trump said, 'I just want to make sure I go to heaven today.'I thought, 'Wow, that's amazing.'The president of the United States—it is on his heart: 'If something happens, I just want to make sure that I make heaven.'There's a stirring in him.

