What do you want to call them, the president's kids? Is that what you call them?

00:28:51.951 --> 00:28:56.862
I don't know. That sounds odd, doesn't it? 'Kids.'Is that 'first lady,''first kids'?

00:28:56.863 --> 00:29:06.959
I don't know. First, first... it works. That's what we're going to say: they're the first kids.

00:29:06.960 --> 00:29:16.957
We're going to pray God puts a hedge around all of them, even the first grandkids. You know, it works. It's serious.

00:29:16.958 --> 00:29:24.393
But I believe God's got His hand on all the firsts, and He's got it on the seconds and the thirds.

00:29:24.394 --> 00:29:28.959
I know He has a plan for each one of us, but I know that this is not the end of the end.

00:29:28.960 --> 00:29:35.910
We're going to see a great harvest of souls, and I'm believing God for a financial harvest for our family.

00:29:35.911 --> 00:29:42.900
