00:29:42.901 --> 00:29:50.939
And I just keep believing that God's got this, and He has not brought us this far to fail.

00:29:50.940 --> 00:29:56.455
His hand is not short, and in all this that I keep seeing, He's going to always provide.

00:29:56.456 --> 00:30:02.711
Braden brought it up. He said, 'Daddy, do you remember when you saw the people praying around the table?

00:30:02.712 --> 00:30:12.468
There was no food in the pots.'And there was a whole bunch of them in this time of prayer.

00:30:12.469 --> 00:30:18.959
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to supernaturally provide for My people.

00:30:18.960 --> 00:30:35.162
