00:38:03.949 --> 00:38:17.916
Use your faith for something small and believe God for it. For when hard, trying times come, you won't faint. This won't take you over.

00:38:17.918 --> 00:38:28.520
You practice now because you practice while times are good and there's plenty, so that you don't freak out when things are a little shaky and you go, 'Oh, no.

00:38:28.521 --> 00:38:34.785
No.'There's no 'Oh, no.'We're good. God is good in the good times and God is good in the bad times.

