00:39:55.358 --> 00:40:02.412
I may have a bad day, but I don't stay in that bad day.'I don't stay in the bad day.

00:40:02.413 --> 00:40:09.462
I choose to follow Jesus in good and in bad, on the mountain or in the valley.

00:40:09.463 --> 00:40:18.099
Do you understand? God's still God, and he's God on the mountain and he's God in the valley. I love that song.

00:40:18.100 --> 00:40:28.959
