This is right before the tribulation. This is the beginning of sorrows, the great birthing pains.

00:41:23.316 --> 00:41:31.173
This is 'as the days of Noah, so will it be.'This is where we are and headed.

00:41:31.174 --> 00:41:36.464
And a lot of people do not realize how much we will see before the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:41:36.465 --> 00:41:48.559
