00:44:09.599 --> 00:44:18.159
For the first time ever, you don't realize the prayer covering the church, the body of Christ, brings.

00:44:18.160 --> 00:44:25.878
The great restrainer—us, the church, the ones that are radical and on fire—were taken out of here.

00:44:25.879 --> 00:44:39.358
And for the first time ever, that prayer covering that was over the world that we bring every day when we do these videos and you pray in your own time, you bring a peace over the earth by your prayers.

00:44:39.359 --> 00:44:46.799
The prayers of the righteous availeth much. Remember this.

00:44:46.800 --> 00:44:53.759
Remember what I'm trying to tell you, because you still have a window of opportunity to get your heart right.

00:44:53.760 --> 00:45:01.919
I remember, and I was there, and each year the Lord took me into the years of tribulation of how bad it truly gets.

00:45:01.920 --> 00:45:08.176
And the further tribulation, the seven years—the first three and a half years was not that bad.

00:45:08.177 --> 00:45:19.996
It was terrible compared to where we are right now, but the last was unbearable. I'm talking bugs. There it was. It was awful.

00:45:19.997 --> 00:45:31.199
It looked like your worst movie you could ever think of, some kind of sci-fi, and it was like something out of that with hailstones falling out of the sky.

00:45:31.200 --> 00:45:44.318
