00:45:55.920 --> 00:46:07.519
All of a sudden that chip comes, and they inject that chip inside of you in your forehead or your hand, and all of a sudden they go and they're like stone cold. They lose everything. I'll never forget it.

00:46:07.520 --> 00:46:16.159
