00:46:21.440 --> 00:46:29.315
And I saw it, and more people did not want to take that chip. When you took it, it made you a zombie.

00:46:29.316 --> 00:46:47.596
But the rioting and all the looting stopped because they had a chip in their hand and they had a chip in their forehead, and they became like a zombie, and all the looting and all the rioting and the murdering and all the craziness stopped.

00:46:47.597 --> 00:46:56.016
