00:47:07.440 --> 00:47:12.078
But there were groups of people, pockets of people that were resistant.

00:47:12.079 --> 00:47:19.439
But they couldn't resist because the guns they had were like little things that just knocked them out cold.

00:47:19.440 --> 00:47:27.933
It wasn't like what you think. The drones told everything you did. There were drones always.

00:47:27.934 --> 00:47:35.869
The sky sounded like it was buzzing around, and everything was always alive in the sky by the thousands of drones—tens of thousands.

00:47:35.870 --> 00:47:44.566
And they're always flying. And people think, 'Well, we'll just get away from that.'Nobody is going to hide from what I saw coming.

00:47:44.567 --> 00:47:53.019
It's not like the movies they try to make of it. No, they dug in the side of hills, in the side of the Ozarks, and in the mountains trying to hide.

00:47:53.020 --> 00:48:00.630
But the winters were so bad because the weather was so bad, with things happening with the weather, you couldn't eat.

00:48:00.631 --> 00:48:06.862
They starved to death in the side of these mountains. They starved to death.

00:48:06.863 --> 00:48:12.221
There was no water. The water was polluted. There was no way to get clean water.

00:48:12.222 --> 00:48:14.729
It was wormwood. Remember, think about what the Bible talks about wormwood.

00:48:14.730 --> 00:48:19.142
The water was bad. You couldn't drink the water; the water was making people sick.

00:48:19.143 --> 00:48:23.256
So you couldn't drink purified water; there was no way to get purifying tablets.

00:48:23.257 --> 00:48:32.239
And if you had a fire, the drones would see it and they would find you, and then they would send the authorities there and you were dead anyway.

00:48:32.240 --> 00:48:38.451
So if you don't serve Jesus now with all your heart, you're not going to serve him in the end times.

00:48:38.452 --> 00:48:43.358
All these people say, 'Well, I don't believe in the rapture.'You better.

00:48:43.359 --> 00:48:50.033
You better. That's all I've got to say. You better. All these people saying, 'Well, we're going to live.

00:48:50.034 --> 00:48:56.233
We're going to be just fine. Christians are going to...'No, they're going to die. They're going to die.

00:48:56.234 --> 00:49:01.550
Not that death is a bad thing, but I'm telling you this: I don't want nobody cutting my head off.

